{
  "text": "Finally, some effort has been spent on the construction of schemes for verifiable computation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , which aim at outsourcing computations to a third party, while offering a proof of correctness for the result. At the moment, these constructions are rather impractical and cannot cope with side-effects of the program execution.",
